==English==
===Etymology===
From Japanese [[忍者]] ([[にんじゃ]], ninja).
===Noun===
'''ninja''' (''Plural:'' '''ninja''' or [[ninjas]])

# A person trained primarily in [[stealth]], [[espionage]] and [[assassination]].

===Verb===

'''ninja'''
# Stealing something in [[MMORPG]] which originally belongs to other players, especially about [[loot]].

